                                                                                                                                Buttons

                                                                                                                                Button group

                                                                                                                                Stable

                                                                                                                                A button group is a collection of buttons combined to allow users to filter content, make selections, or trigger actions.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Specs
                                                                                                                                Status & changelog

                                                                                                                                Metrics

                                                                                                                                The style of the button will dictate its spacing relative to other buttons in its group. Pill and Circle buttons need 8 spacing between each other and Rectangular and Square buttons need 0 spacing.

                                                                                                                                Pill and circle button groups

                                                                                                                                Pill and circle-shaped buttons per their shape require spacing between them. The default is 8.

                                                                                                                                Circle button spacing
                                                                                                                                Pill button spacing

                                                                                                                                Clustered button spacing

                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                The vertical spacing between rows in a cluster is 12 instead of 8 to accommodate the touch target minimums.

                                                                                                                                Rect and Square button groups

                                                                                                                                Rect and square-shaped buttons sit close to one another and require 1 spacing between them.

                                                                                                                                Rect button spacing
                                                                                                                                Square button spacing


                                                                                                                                Spacing in a mobile header

                                                                                                                                Button groups in a header have 16 padding top and bottom (visually).

                                                                                                                                Note: due to the min target area of smaller buttons the actual spacing = 10 + 6 from the min target area for a total visual height of 16.

                                                                                                                                Button group in header
                                                                                                                                Pinned with header

                                                                                                                                Type and color

                                                                                                                                See button specs for type and color.

                                                                                                                                "Gluten free, Button."

                                                                                                                                Label: [Button label]

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button


                                                                                                                                2. Voiced preview:

                                                                                                                                "Healthy, Button."

                                                                                                                                Label: [Button label]

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button


                                                                                                                                3. Voiced preview:

                                                                                                                                "Selected, Large, Button."

                                                                                                                                Label: [Button label]

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button, Selected


                                                                                                                                Notes: Append the trait Selected to a button when toggled on
